id":"14328890212c10a1b5de1bba4ac4d9ebfccd6de1","tid":911110,"uid":40709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:33:50.000Z","msg":"樓主講咗永遠飛行模式<br />\n淨係第一段<br />\n<br />\n等我飲醉酒<br />\n你要解釋 等我飲醉酒<br />\n我也許 不會 深究<br />\n隨時重獲你自由<br />\n<br />\n尋日朝一出 一聽<br />\n你 噏 乜 鳩 呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好在三部曲前兩部都過得去<br />\n呢隻就爭啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f372bbb7abb894cd062af3b7c806ac5e77d1b2e6","tid":911110,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"2E2F 點入到HKU<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55888c602aa27dcd954c21aa8a679afb9a80641a","tid":911110,"uid":15394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b0206edfce2b35ad6e09f79c42cd6c059b47811e","tid":911110,"uid":212124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a4a5176458ae34d2803b7c96bba2930d9aec68d","tid":911110,"uid":56544,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:27:14.000Z","msg":"首龍舌蘭 一聽覺得歌詞怪怪地<br />\n詞不達意 咩mood都冇晒<br />\n又嘥左eason一首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:32:03.000Z","msg":"呢個真，其實我都只係今日先聽首歌，melody chord同編曲係廣東歌黎講算好出色，夠哂張力，eason又唱得好，詞真係配唔上編曲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:37:11.000Z","msg":"我見有個post吹奏呢首歌，<br />\n係moov dl完，覺得首曲幾有一絲不掛既味道，<br />\n但之後聽哂成首就del左，<br />\n啲詞太垃圾"},{"pid":"8e435f867f63b4d5ad05664c86f10688845f2759","tid":911110,"uid":192409,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:37:50.000Z","msg":"CE25 點解可以跌到AL2E2F<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8dbc97437d8bc85ad2d3d82998f7ab5b2ca93db","tid":911110,"uid":44807,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"最好笑係佢主持世界盃節目，讀錯埃及做&quot;挨&quot;及，比Keyman直接串佢：你填詞架喎，讀&quot;挨&quot;及? 埃(哀)及啊嘛。佢真係無料到，識多些少中文都好過佢，鍾志光中文水準都屌打佢。"},{"pid":"28301077cadc8e91153ab564047f58c919ed91d2","tid":911110,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T16:55:32.000Z","msg":"搭上YY<br />\n氣勢一時無兩"},{"pid":"bf6222c4201d9f61ac43f666c7023c5fff67b928","tid":911110,"uid":15394,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T17:15:12.000Z","msg":"同埋條友既中文水平真係好低 好平庸<br />\n淨係首龍舌蘭不停我 我 我 都想死<br />\n其他詞亦然，去到副歌位你竟然比啲咁垃圾既詞出黎！？<br />\n例子 漸漸我 甚麼都不想知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外佢成日想學wyman既直述又唔得，<br />\n又想學林夕既講下佛，緣，永恆，孽，<br />\n但高深野又未夠班，<br />\n<br />\n仲有另一個style，<br />\n想學周耀輝既逐粒字登出黎，去營造意景<br />\n例如 周耀輝 還有什麼可以送給你<br />\n「送過你<span style=\"color: red;\">一剎</span>　<span style=\"color: red;\">透明</span><br />\n也送過你<span style=\"color: red;\">一串</span>　<span style=\"color: red;\">蛻變</span><br />\n我送過你<span style=\"color: red;\">一片</span>　<span style=\"color: red;\">藍天空</span><br />\n或者未來難做到　<span style=\"color: red;\">更完美</span><br />\n<br />\n送過你<span style=\"color: red;\">一次</span>　<span style=\"color: red;\">旅程</span><br />\n也送過你<span style=\"color: red;\">一個</span>　<span style=\"color: red;\">世界</span><br />\n我送過你<span style=\"color: red;\">一切</span>　<span style=\"color: red;\">舊記憶</span><br />\n或者目前沉悶得　<span style=\"color: red;\">接近死</span>」<br />\n<br />\n但到陳詠謙呢，就fail，變左柒味<br />\n例子 漸漸<br />\n「在夜晚 說早晨<br />\n閒談後 你更像別人<br />\n字幕裡 說冬日灰暗<br />\n回答你 這邊的氣氛<br />\n<br />\n就像你 已記不起了<br />\n連懷舊 也格外寂寥<br />\n雜物裡 遺物和舊照<br />\n誰變賣 誰棄掉 誰看到破曉」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （後面句副歌我覺得真係平庸到不得了）<br />\n<br />\n結果就好似成為一個亂9拋書包，<br />\n又想叫春既mk仔打instagram status <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3d72ae7d379ce8d875ada437b8afc18ee8332d","tid":911110,"uid":179935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T20:29